            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/2256-Step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a wide, large based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced mushrooms</strong>, <strong>red onion</strong> and <strong>red pepper</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until starting to caramelise</p>\n<p> </p>",
